<i>adverb</i>: 깜빡깜빡 [깜빡깜빡], 깜빡 [깜빡], 깜박깜박 [깜박깜박], 깜박 [깜박] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>깜빡깜빡 [깜빡깜빡]</dt><br>
<dd>1. with repeated flashes</dd><br>
<dd>불빛이 자꾸 밝았다가 어두워지거나 어두웠다가 밝아지는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the manner of a source of light brightening and then going dim, or dimming and then going bright repeatedly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. with repeated blinks</dd><br>
<dd>눈을 자꾸 감았다 뜨는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the manner of opening and closing one's eyes repeatedly.</dd><br>
<dd>3. forgetfully</dd><br>
<dd>기억이나 의식 등이 잠깐씩 자꾸 흐려지는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of one's memory or consciousness being dim or lost over and over again.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>깜빡 [깜빡]</dt><br>
<dd>1. with a flash</dd><br>
<dd>불빛이 밝았다가 잠깐 어두워지거나 어두웠다가 잠깐 밝아지는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word mimicking the manner of a source of light brigtening and then going dim, or dimming and then going bright in quick succession.</dd><br>
<dd>2. with a blink</dd><br>
<dd>눈을 잠깐 감았다 뜨는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word mimicking the manner of closing one's eyes momentarily before opening.</dd><br>
<dd>3. forgetfully</dd><br>
<dd>기억이나 의식 등이 잠깐 흐려지는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of one's memory or conciousness being dim or lost.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>깜박깜박 [깜박깜박]</dt><br>
<dd>1. with repeated flashes</dd><br>
<dd>불빛이 자꾸 밝았다가 어두워지거나 어두웠다가 밝아지는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the manner of a source of light brightening and then going dim, or dimming and then going bright repeatedly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. with repeated blinks</dd><br>
<dd>눈을 자꾸 감았다 뜨는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the manner of opening and closing one's eyes repeatedly.</dd><br>
<dd>3. forgetfully</dd><br>
<dd>기억이나 의식 등이 잠깐씩 자꾸 흐려지는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of losing one's memory or having only dim consciousness again and again.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>깜박 [깜박]</dt><br>
<dd>1. with a flash</dd><br>
<dd>불빛이 밝았다가 잠깐 어두워지거나 어두웠다가 잠깐 밝아지는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the manner of a source of light brightening and then going dim, or dimming and then going bright in quick succession.</dd><br>
<dd>2. with a blink</dd><br>
<dd>눈을 잠깐 감았다 뜨는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the manner of closing one's eyes momentarily before opening.</dd><br>
<dd>3. forgetfully</dd><br>
<dd>기억이나 의식 등이 잠깐 흐려지는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of one's memory or consciousness being dim or lost.</dd><br>
